{"data":[{"date":"09:24 18/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chievo vs Juventus 23h00 ng\u00e0y 18/8 (Serie A 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-chievo-vs-juventus-23h00-ngay-188-serie-a-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chievo vs Juventus l\u00fac 23h00 ng\u00e0y 18/8 (V\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Italia Serie A 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chievo vs Juventus 23h00 ng\u00e0y 188 Serie A 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chievo vs Juventus 23h00 ng\u00e0y 188 Serie A 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/chievo-juventus-480.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chievo vs Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span>Chievo vs Juventus: 0-3<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nJuventus v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a H\u00e8 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1. Bianconeri ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi tr\u00ean TTCN \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 Juventus Arena nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh m\u00e0 gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n mi\u00eau t\u1ea3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m CLB. Trong \u0111\u00f3, d\u0129 nhi\u00ean ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mang t\u00ean Ronaldo. S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a CR7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1n s\u1ed1t mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i l\u1eabn chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cho Bianconeri. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1c Juventini, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tifosi, m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juve \u0111\u00eam nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3, Juventus c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c. Lichtsteiner ra \u0111i th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Cancelo thay th\u1ebf. S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Juventus nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n b\u1ed9i ph\u1ea7n. \u1ede h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, Emre Can c\u0169ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap gia t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Bianconeri. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay \u1edf Liverpool m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Can c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Khedira h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m hay b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t Serie A m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. \u1ede tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, Juve c\u0169ng gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Dybala. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Bonucci. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00f3m l\u1ea1i, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y HLV Max Allegri \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Juve \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t ra ngo\u00e0i bi\u00ean gi\u1edbi Italia, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c s\u00e1nh ngang v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Real Madrid, Barcelona hay Man City. Juventus \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea1nh, \u0111\u00eam nay Allegri c\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ngay t\u1eeb v\u1ea1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. Danh s\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u01a1ng binh c\u1ee7a Bianconeri th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Leonardo Spinazzola.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00e0ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n v\u1edbi Juve khi h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u1eb9 k\u00fd nh\u01b0 Chievo \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Marc\u2019Antonio Bentegodi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trung y\u1ebfu \u1edf Serie A. M\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Chievo c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u0169ng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Juventus ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n. Trong 10 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Chievo g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Juventus b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, gi\u00e0nh t\u1edbi 9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf, Bianconeri s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN<br>\r\nChievo th\u1eafng 13, thua 5/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1. <br>\r\n11/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chievo c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung. <br>\r\nJuventus th\u1eafng 10, thua 9/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1. <br>\r\n11/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Juventus c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u1ebb<br>\r\n15/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chievo c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u1ebb. 7/9 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chievo c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. Tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5622","checkdouble":"194720"},{"date":"09:27 18/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Lazio vs Napoli 01h30 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (Serie A 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-lazio-vs-napoli-01h30-ngay-198-serie-a-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lazio vs Napoli l\u00fac 01h30 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (V\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Italia Serie A 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Lazio vs Napoli 01h30 ng\u00e0y 198 Serie A 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Lazio vs Napoli 01h30 ng\u00e0y 198 Serie A 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/lazio-napoli.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lazio vs Napoli</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span>Lazio vs Napoli:\u00a03-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Khi HLV Ancelotti chia tay Milan v\u00e0 Serie A v\u00e0o H\u00e8 2009, Juventus v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, Cristiano Ronaldo c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid, trong khi Simone Inzaghi \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p\u2026 <br>\r\n<br>\r\n9 n\u0103m tr\u00f4i qua, Carletto \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League (c\u00f9ng Chelsea), Ligue 1 (PSG) v\u00e0 Bundesliga (Bayern) c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u00fap Real Madrid ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t 12 n\u0103m c\u01a1n kh\u00e1t Champions League v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2013/14. 9 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7y s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a HLV Ancelotti \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i, Serie A \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn bi\u1ebft bao \u0111\u1ed5i thay, t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3 th\u00ea th\u1ea3m sau khi m\u1ea5t Zlatan Ibrahimovic v\u00e0 Kaka (c\u00f9ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2009 khi Carletto chia tay Milan) cho t\u1edbi m\u00e0n t\u00e1i sinh c\u1ee7a Juve \u1edf Champions League, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn nay l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNapoli \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 16/18 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a trong 6 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Lazio, trong \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-1. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Napoli tr\u01b0\u1edbc Lazio d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Maurizio Sarri kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho h\u1ecd m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00eam nay. D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eeba h\u01b0\u1edfng di s\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 s\u1ed9 t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Sarri, HLV Ancelotti v\u1eabn g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNapoli kh\u00f4ng t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1ed3 \u1ea1t nh\u01b0 Juventus, Milan v\u00e0 Inter. Ch\u00ednh s\u1ef1 c\u0169 k\u1ef9 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Napoli kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch sung s\u1ee9c, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u00f2n t\u00e2m l\u00fd ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n sau khi tu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t Scudetto m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. <br>\r\nGi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Napoli trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Ngay tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u00e1 c\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Napoli c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n Lazio ch\u00fat \u00edt, tr\u00e1i h\u1eb3n v\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ea7y ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean v\u00e0o m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a HLV Simone Inzaghi, Lazio l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 nh\u1ea5t Serie A m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi 89 b\u00e0n/38 tr\u1eadn. Lazio \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Felipe Anderson, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Luis Alberto, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t m\u1edbi l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 n\u00e3o trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4. Trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00f3n ti\u1ebfp Napoli \u0111\u00eam nay, Lazio h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn 90 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ed1c l\u1eeda. T\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng s\u1ef1 u\u1ec3 o\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Napoli sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 H\u00e8, Lazio c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng cho HLV Ancelotti m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Serie A!<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN XUNG QUANH<br>\r\n- Lazio: V\u1eafng Lulic, Patric, Leiva (treo gi\u00f2). Murgia, Berisha (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng).<br>\r\n- Napoli: V\u1eafng Meret, Ghoulam, Younes (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng).<br>\r\n- Theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Lazio th\u1eafng 6, h\u00f2a 1, thua 4/11 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y; th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 1, thua 2/6 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n- Theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Napoli th\u1eafng 3, thua 9/12 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Serie A; th\u1eafng 2, thua 5/7 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nT\u00e0i n\u1ed5 c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn<br>\r\n6/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Napoli, 8/11 tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Lazio v\u00e0 5/7 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean. Tin cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u01b0a g\u00f4n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5621","checkdouble":"194721"},{"date":"09:30 18/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Guingamp vs PSG 22h00 ng\u00e0y 18/8 (Ligue 1 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-guingamp-vs-psg-22h00-ngay-188-ligue-1-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Guingamp vs PSG l\u00fac 22h00 ng\u00e0y 18/8 (V\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Ph\u00e1p Ligue 1 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Guingamp vs PSG 22h00 ng\u00e0y 188 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Guingamp vs PSG 22h00 ng\u00e0y 188 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/guingamp-psg-480.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Guingamp vs PSG</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Guingamp vs PSG: 1-3<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nHLV Antoine Kombouare ch\u1eb3ng xa l\u1ea1 g\u00ec v\u1edbi PSG. \u00d4ng t\u1eebng thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf PSG c\u1ea3 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 (kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG 5 n\u0103m, t\u1eeb 1990-1995) l\u1eabn tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV (2009-2011). Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 54 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00fap Guingamp gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc PSG trong su\u1ed1t 8 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t 2 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nhau. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 2-1 t\u1ea1i Roudourou \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Ligue 1 2016/17.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, t\u00e2n HLV Thomas Tuchel kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00e0o v\u1ebft xe \u0111\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y, t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. Do v\u1eady, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Guingamp l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Tuchel. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSo v\u1edbi g\u1ea7n 2 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Guingamp g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i, nh\u01b0ng PSG l\u1ea1i kh\u00e1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. G\u00e3 nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0u th\u00e0nh Paris \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n th\u00eam 2 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi: Neymar v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe. C\u1ea3 hai s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf chuy\u1ebfn vi\u1ebfng th\u0103m s\u00e2n Roudourou \u0111\u00eam nay. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Edinson Cavani (\u0111ang ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng) li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u201ch\u00e0nh h\u1ea1\u201d h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Guingamp, thay nhau ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o (m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o 1 b\u00e0n) \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00eam nay, Cavani kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Tr\u00e1m v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 Mbappe. Gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u1edf m\u00e0n t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 19 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a H\u00e8 r\u1ef1c s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. T\u1eebng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong t\u1ea1i Monaco v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh PSG m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a s\u0103n m\u1edbi c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4. \u1ede tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Caen 3-0 (v\u00f2ng 1), Neymar \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n t\u1edbi PSG v\u00e0 anh \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t hay. C\u00f2n trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, Mbappe s\u1ebd t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Tuchel.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t PSG ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n d\u1ea7n qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Cavani thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng; m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Neymar hay Mbappe c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn vai tr\u00f2 n\u00e0y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN<br>\r\nTheo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Guingamp th\u1eafng 10, h\u00f2a 2, thua 8 \u1edf 20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t; PSG th\u1eafng 6, thua 14 \u1edf 20 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\nTr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Guingamp th\u1eafng 9, h\u00f2a 2, thua 9 \u1edf 20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\nTr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, PSG th\u1eafng 6, thua 14 \u1edf 20 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nL\u01b0\u1edbi rung cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 8 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i, 5/6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Guingamp v\u00e0 7/9 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 71-90. V\u00ec v\u1eady, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00eam nay s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung 20 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5620","checkdouble":"194722"},{"date":"11:23 18/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Drochtersen vs Bayern Munich 20h30 ng\u00e0y 18/8 (C\u00fap QG \u0110\u1ee9c 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-drochtersen-vs-bayern-munich-20h30-ngay-188-cup-qg-duc-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Drochtersen vs Bayern Munich l\u00fac 20h30 ng\u00e0y 18/8 (C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Drochtersen vs Bayern Munich 20h30 ng\u00e0y 188 C\u00fap QG \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Drochtersen vs Bayern Munich 20h30 ng\u00e0y 188 C\u00fap QG \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/Drochtersen-vs-Bayern-Munich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Drochtersen vs Bayern Munich</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Drochtersen vs Bayern Munich: 0-6<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Th\u1ef1c ra, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 v\u1edbi Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 tu\u1ea7n, b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap QG. H\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n HLV Niko Kovac \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Frankfurd 5-0. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d \u0111\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u201cn\u00f3ng m\u00e1y\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y NHM x\u1ee9 Bavaria r\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng n\u1eefa t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c, khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 h\u1ecd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 Drochtersen, CLB v\u00f4 danh ti\u1ec3u t\u1ed1t \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng 4 \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 HLV Kovac ch\u1ec9 tung ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb th\u00ec ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi tay CLB s\u1ed1 1 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV\u00a0Kovac \u0111\u00e3 \u00fap m\u1edf v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 v\u1eady Bayern Munich s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-0 nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chemnitzer FC \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 C\u00fap QG \u0110\u1ee9c m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nDrochtersen (4-2-3-1): Siefkes; Rogowski, El Saleh, Behrmann, Klee; Mau, St\u00f6hr; Nagel, Z\u00f6pfgen, Goo\u00dfen; Andrijanic.<br>\r\nBayern Munich (4-2-3-1): Neuer; Hummels, Suele, Kimmich, Alaba; Thiago, Martinez; Mueller, Robben, Ribery; Lewandowski.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5619","checkdouble":"194730"},{"date":"10:21 18/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca vs Alaves (3h15 ng\u00e0y 19/8): Cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-barca-vs-alaves-3h15-ngay-198-cuoc-dua-bat-dau.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Alaves c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed9i nghi\u1ec7p nh\u1ea5t \u1edf La Liga l\u00fac n\u00e0y khi h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Barcelona \u0111ang h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf sau m\u00f9a h\u00e8 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ea7y th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</h2><h2>Tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Barca<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Barcelona khi h\u1ecd b\u1ed5 sung b\u1ed1n b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb. Sau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga, HLV Ernesto Valverde v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau xa h\u01a1n, cao h\u01a1n l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League - gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ecd b\u1ed1n m\u00f9a li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca vs Alaves (3h15 ng\u00e0y 198) Cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca vs Alaves (3h15 ng\u00e0y 198) Cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Nhan-dinh-Barca-vs-Alaves-(3h15-ngay-198)-Cuoc-dua-bat-dau-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca vs Alaves nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t chi\u1ec1u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLionel Messi tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n La Liga th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1ed1i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Barca m\u00f9a n\u00e0y l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 mang \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Barca. Ngo\u00e0i Rakitic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia, ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Barca nh\u01b0 Pique, Coutinho, Busquets, Messi v\u00e0 Luis Suarez \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u1ea3i qua th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u00f9ng Barca. Tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sevilla \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau C\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha, tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n g\u1eb7p Alaves l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Barca ch\u1ee9ng minh h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca vo dich Sieu cup TBN\" title=\"Barca vo dich Sieu cup TBN\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/5-diem-nhan-sevilla-12-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Barca kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a n\u00e0y, La Liga b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n khi Barca nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ng\u1ef1a v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch. Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111ang c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n, trong khi Atletico Madrid ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 k\u1ebb th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c, ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 s\u00e1nh vai v\u1edbi Barca trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch nh\u01b0 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Diego Simeone.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho Alaves?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">So v\u1edbi Barca, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n Alaves chi ra cho chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ebfn 9 t\u00e2n binh. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Alaves m\u00f9a n\u00e0y t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1eed th\u00e1ch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Barca tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Nou Camp. HLV Abelardo Fernandez ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng cho Alaves nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ernesto Valverde.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Barca vs Alaves\" title=\"Preview Barca vs Alaves\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/Preview-Barca-vs-Alaves.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca vs Alaves - C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch?</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGuidetti ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Alaves khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Nou Camp v\u00e0o n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Valverde l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, nhi\u1ec1u m\u0169i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 tr\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o c\u1eb7p Messi - Suarez nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Coutinho, Dembele hay Malcom s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV Valverde tri\u1ec3n khai nhi\u1ec1u m\u0169i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u1eb1m ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Abelardo. N\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c, Barca ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn ba \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Alaves.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Barca th\u1eafng 28 trong 31 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf La Liga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Barca th\u1eafng 9 trong 10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Alaves tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Barca ghi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u00e0n \u1edf 9 trong 10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Alaves \u1edf m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Barca b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi 16 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, 3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a, ghi 53 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 11 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Barca:</strong> Denis Suarez ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ra s\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Alaves:</strong> Rodrigo Ely ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng - Adrian Dieguez th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Barca vs Alaves (3h15 ng\u00e0y 19/8):</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Barca (4-3-3):</strong> 1.Stegen - 20.S.Roberto, 3.Pique, 15.Lenglet, 18.J.Alba - 7.Coutinho, 5.Busquets, 4.Rakitic - 10.Messi, 9.Suarez, 11.Dembele</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Alaves (4-4-2):</strong> 1.Pacheco - 21.Aguirregabiria, 15.Navarro, 5.Laguardia, 3.Duarte - 23.Jony, 19.Garcia, 22.Wakaso, 11.Gomez - 10.Guidetti, 7.Sobrino</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1:</strong> Barca 4-1 Alaves<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Barcelona vs Alaves\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Barcelona vs Alaves\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/Barca-vs-Alaves-(4-3-3-vs-4-4-2).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Barcelona vs Alaves</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Barca m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-barcelona-thanh-minh-cho-phong-do-sa-sut-cua-luis-suarez-172-194570.html\">HLV Barcelona thanh minh cho phong \u0111\u1ed9 sa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Luis Suarez</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-se-khong-ban-pogba-cho-barca-172-194472.html\">MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Pogba cho Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/roma-chuan-bi-bao-thu-barca-thanh-cong-180-194430.html\">Roma chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb &ldquo;b\u00e1o th\u00f9&rdquo; Barca th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-muon-mua-rabiot-cua-psg-180-194389.html\">Real l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cu\u1ed7m m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/giai-cuu-barcelona-du-bi-hang-sang-duoc-dam-bao-tuong-lai-180-194378.html\">Gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Barcelona, d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb h\u1ea1ng sang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/5-diem-nhan-sevilla-12-barca-180-194361.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong ng\u00e0y Barca may m\u1eafn gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5618","checkdouble":"194724"},{"date":"09:10 18/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham vs Fulham (21h ng\u00e0y 18/8): C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Kane gi\u1ea3i l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-tottenham-vs-fulham-21h-ngay-188-co-hoi-cho-kane-giai-loi-nguyen.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham d\u00f9 \u0111ang g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Fulham \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111ang ng\u1ed3n ngang h\u01a1n c\u1ea3. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pochettino gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi HLV Pochettino \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n n\u0103m 2014. Spurs kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u00ec v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, &ldquo;G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng&rdquo; v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i \u1edf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 White Hart Lane nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0 v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i thu\u00ea t\u1ea1m s\u00e2n Wembley.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi Tottenham. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf Premier League n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean nh\u01b0ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Minh ch\u1ee9ng r\u00f5 n\u00e9t l\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Newcastle. Spurs th\u1eafng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt t\u1ea1i St. James&rsquo; Park. D\u00f9 tung ra 15 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 5 trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham vs Fulham (21h ng\u00e0y 188) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham vs Fulham (21h ng\u00e0y 188) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/28/Nhan-dinh-Tottenham-vs-Fulham-(21h-ngay-188)-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham vs Fulham:&nbsp;Kane \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u1ea3i l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n th\u00e1ng 8</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Tottenham trong th\u00e1ng 8 l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n. Kane t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean v\u00e0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm ra c\u00e1ch h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i l\u1eddi nguy\u00ean n\u00e0y. Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea cho th\u1ea5y, Kane \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 988 ph\u00fat kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf Premier League trong th\u00e1ng 8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Fulham t\u1ed1i nay, Spurs c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Fulham c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ban b\u1eadt t\u1eeb tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chuy\u1ec1n ng\u1eafn d\u00f9 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. \u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi tri\u1ec3n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1ch \u00e1p s\u00e1t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu c\u1ee7a Tottenham, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Fulham m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, Fulham c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi Crystal Palace m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, The Cottagers chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Jean-Michael Seri, Schurrle hay Mitrovic. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn Fulham ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nX\u00e9t v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u, Tottenham \u0111ang v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i. H\u1ecd th\u1eafng 8/9 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i. Ngo\u00e0i ra, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Spurs r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 thua 2 trong s\u1ed1 38 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Nh\u00ecn chung, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Fulham g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pochettino-du-doan-ve-mot-mua-giai-kho-khan-o-spurs-172-194646.html\">Pochettino d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf Spurs</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/eric-dier-khong-co-tan-binh-tottenham-van-du-suc-vao-top-4-172-194409.html\">Eric Dier: Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh Tottenham v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c v\u00e0o Top 4</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Tottenham vs Fulham:</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Tottenham th\u1eafng 8/9 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i, thua tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i<br>\r\n- L\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Fulham th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Spurs t\u1ea1i White Hart Lane l\u00e0 v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2013 (1-0, Berbatov ghi b\u00e0n)<br>\r\n- Fulham ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 2 trong s\u1ed1 24 tr\u1eadn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Spurs t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh<br>\r\n- Harry Kane ghi hat-trick trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 c\u1ee7a Tottenham t\u1ea1i Craven Cottage khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 2/2017<br>\r\n- Kane ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ghi b\u00e0n trong th\u00e1ng 8 \u1edf Premier League d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i 14 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 s\u00fat 46 l\u1ea7n<br>\r\n- Tottenham \u0111ang b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 36 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc QPR v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 4/2012<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Tottenham vs Fulham\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Tottenham vs Fulham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/Tottenham-vs-Fulham-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-3-3).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Tottenham vs Fulham</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1: 2-0</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5617","checkdouble":"194718"},{"date":"10:09 18/08","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Sanchez kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \"bom x\u1ecbt\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/nguoi-cu-mu-khang-dinh-sanchez-khong-phai-bom-xit.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Wes Brown kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Alexis Sanchez v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u201cbom x\u1ecbt\u201d c\u1ee7a Man United.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng si\u00eau sao Alexis Sanchez t\u1eeb Arsenal \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile ch\u01b0a thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSanchez kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man United. Anh ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n sau 18 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Alexis Sanchez kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i bom x\u1ecbt h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Alexis Sanchez kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i bom x\u1ecbt h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/Nguoi-cu-MU-khang-dinh-Alexis-Sanchez-khong-phai-bom-xit-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Wes Brown kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Alexis Sanchez kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \"bom x\u1ecbt\" c\u1ee7a MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Wes Brown tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Sanchez s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng minh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Daily Star, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU cho bi\u1ebft: <em>\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c MU mua Sanchez l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 sai l\u1ea7m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Sanchez l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf Arsenal. Ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp. V\u00e0 sau 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00fang v\u1ec1 Sanchez. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n theo th\u1eddi gian\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Sanchez trong th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c \u1edf Man United. Martial l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t v\u00ec m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i th\u00edch Martial. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 lu\u00f4n \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMartial l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 ch\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u \u00e1c li\u1ec7t. Man United \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 MU:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pogba-dang-le-phai-lam-doi-truong-man-utd-tu-luc-moi-ve-172-194712.html\">Pogba \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Man Utd t\u1eeb l\u00fac m\u1edbi v\u1ec1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-mu-doi-ban-quach-pogba-di-vi-thai-do-172-194664.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU \u0111\u00f2i b\u00e1n qu\u00e1ch Pogba \u0111i v\u00ec th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5616","checkdouble":"194719"},{"date":"10:20 18/08","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00f3i l\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Ozil","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/huyen-thoai-bao-ve-thoi-luoi-phong-ngu-cua-ozil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Kanu cho r\u1eb1ng Arsenal c\u1ea7n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Ozil ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Ozil \u0111ang b\u1ecb s\u0103m soi k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng sau v\u1ee5 l\u00f9m x\u00f9m khi\u1ebfn anh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c. Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Arsenal, Ozil b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Kanu \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Ozil. Anh cho r\u1eb1ng Arsenal n\u00ean t\u1eadp trung ph\u00e1t huy s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Ozil thay v\u00ec b\u1eaft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kanu b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Ozil tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec th\u00f3i l\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kanu b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Ozil tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec th\u00f3i l\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/huyen-thoai-bao-ve-thoi-luoi-phong-ngu-cua-ozil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kanu b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Ozil tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00e1c nhau. \u0110i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Ozil ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Ozil c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn th\u00ec b\u1ea1n n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i. Ban kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Maradona hay Messi ph\u1ea3i lui v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecd t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft l\u00e0m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00ec HLV ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a theo n\u00f3 v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Ozil ph\u00e1t huy s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft t\u1ea1i sao m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Ozil l\u00e0 thi tho\u1ea3ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu t\u1eadp trung. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nOzil v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c mang t\u00ean Chelsea. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Man City, Ozil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n cho Arsenal. Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 v\u1eadt v\u1edd m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Emery \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-chelsea-vs-arsenal-23h30-ngay-188-dung-lay-man-city-lam-thuoc-do-172-194717.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal (23h30 ng\u00e0y 18/8): \u0110\u1eebng l\u1ea5y Man City l\u00e0m th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111o</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-arsenal-da-deu-thay-cu-wenger-khong-biet-huan-luyen-172-194710.html\">Sao Arsenal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Wenger kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5615","checkdouble":"194723"},{"date":"11:04 18/08","title":"\"Pochettino s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft MU\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/18/pochettino-se-khong-tu-choi-neu-duoc-moi-dan-dat-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Jermain Jenas cho r\u1eb1ng HLV Pochettino s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Tottenham \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Man United n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Pochettino \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi sau khi \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i Premier League. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn Tottenham tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean cho m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong top 4 Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Pochettino t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real thay cho Zidane. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pochettino s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pochettino s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/pochettino-se-khong-tu-choi-neu-duoc-moi-dan-dat-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Pochettino kh\u00e1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Man United</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJermain Jenas tin r\u1eb1ng Los Blancos c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00f4i k\u00e9o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pochettino n\u1ebfu g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Spurs c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Pochettino kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ea1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb Man United n\u1ebfu Mourinho ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Pochettino \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian. \u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch l\u1edbn. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Pochettino r\u1ea5t th\u00edch nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c th\u1eed th\u00e1ch nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Man United v\u00e0 Real Madrid m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Pochettino.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cJurgen Klopp s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u ngo\u00e0i Liverpool. Chelsea thay \u0111\u1ed5i HLV h\u00e0ng n\u0103m. N\u1ebfu \u00f4ng \u1ea5y d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea th\u00ec m\u1ecdi c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u1edf Spurs coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed5 s\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 h\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPochettino c\u0169ng t\u1eebng n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn Barcelona v\u00ec c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t cho Espanyol. V\u00ec v\u1eady, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn d\u00e0nh cho Pochettino. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Bayern, PSG v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League ho\u1eb7c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i La Liga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu Mourinho r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Man United, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Pochettino quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf Spurs, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u1edf l\u1ea1i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 MU:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-cu-mu-khang-dinh-sanchez-khong-phai-bom-xit-172-194719.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Sanchez kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i bom x\u1ecbt</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pogba-dang-le-phai-lam-doi-truong-man-utd-tu-luc-moi-ve-172-194712.html\">Pogba \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Man Utd t\u1eeb l\u00fac m\u1edbi v\u1ec1</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5614","checkdouble":"194725"},{"date":"07:26 18/08","title":"Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus: H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh 15 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi l\u00e0ng qu\u00ea Villar Perosa","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/tu-bolton-den-juventus-b-hanh-trinh-su-nghiep-15-nam-cua-cristiano-ronaldo.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung tu\u1ea7n th\u00e1ng T\u00e1m n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u tr\u00f2n 15 n\u0103m ng\u00e0y Cristiano Ronaldo ra m\u1eaft Manchester United trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Bolton Wanderers, di\u1ec7n ki\u1ebfn 67.647 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Old Trafford. C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n sao m\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed7i th\u00e2n quen ch\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 m\u1edbi h\u00f4m qua\u2026</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p Manchester...</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, khi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Sir Alex Ferguson \u0111ang d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1-0, g\u00e3 trai tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i 18 thay th\u1ebf Nicky Butt khu\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea3o b\u00ean \u0111\u00f4i h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00e2n \u01b0\u1edbt ch\u00e2n r\u00e1o c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh Manchester v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n b\u1ed1n ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 12,2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ch\u1ecbu \u00e1p l\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 mang tr\u00ean l\u01b0ng, k\u1ebf th\u1eeba c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i David Beckham.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh 15 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 Villar Perosa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh 15 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 Villar Perosa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Ronaldo-gia-nhap-Juventus-Hanh-trinh-15-nam-ve-Villar-Perosa-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cristiano Ronaldo ra m\u1eaft Manchester United trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bolton c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y tr\u00f2n 15 n\u0103m (16/08/2003)</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh g\u1ea7y nh\u1eb3ng, m\u1eb7t l\u1ea5m t\u1ea5m m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u1ebb b\u1ec1 ngo\u00e0i c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng hay ho g\u00ec m\u1ea5y. M\u1ed9t m\u00e1i t\u00f3c t\u1ed1i m\u00e0u r\u1ed1i b\u1eddi, b\u00f9 x\u00f9 nh\u01b0 t\u1ed5 qu\u1ea1, b\u00f3ng nh\u1eaby nh\u01b0 d\u1ea7u nh\u1edbt v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea9y light b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1i g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00f4i ba s\u1ee3i m\u00ec spaghetti th\u1eeba l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean \u0111\u0129a \u0103n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u1ee5c t\u00ecm v\u00e0 xem l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c video tr\u00ean Youtube v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i Premier League 2003/04 \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn con s\u1ed1 tri\u1ec7u view, ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nghe th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 c\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed3ng ca mang h\u00e0m \u00fd m\u1ec9a mai, ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e1m \u0111\u00f4ng C\u0110V Bolton r\u1ed3i: <strong><em>&ldquo;M\u00e0y l\u00e0 th\u1eb1ng n\u00e0o?&rdquo;</em></strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-den-juventus-canh-chim-bao-bao-cho-ca-serie-a-176-194051.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/ronaldo-11.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-den-juventus-canh-chim-bao-bao-cho-ca-serie-a-176-194051.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus: C\u00e1nh chim b\u00e1o b\u00e3o cho c\u1ea3 Serie A</span><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo nh\u01b0 c\u00e1nh chim b\u00e1o b\u00e3o, b\u00e1o hi\u1ec7u cho s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed5i thay c\u1ee7a Serie A trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 ho\u00e0ng kim.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Nicky Hunt ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t c\u00fa t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o nh\u01b0ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u0169ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, Ronaldo c\u0169ng c\u00f3 l\u1eddi g\u1eedi l\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1eadu nh\u00f3c qu\u00ea m\u00f9a ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1ea3 xung h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed9t kh\u1eafp m\u1eb7t c\u1ecf Old Trafford, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 g\u00e2y ra \u1edf hai b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cristiano mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn c\u00e1i v\u1ed7 m\u1eb7t kh\u00edch l\u1ec7 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Roy Keane. C\u00f3 anh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Man Utd ghi th\u00eam ba b\u00e0n v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh 15 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 Villar Perosa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh 15 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 Villar Perosa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Cristiano-Ronaldo-gia-nhap-Juventus-Hanh-trinh-15-nam-ve-voi-lang-que-Villar-Perosa-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cristiano Ronaldo ra m\u1eaft Manchester United trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bolton c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y tr\u00f2n 15 n\u0103m (16/08/2003)</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Sam Allardyce c\u0169ng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y v\u00e0 ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f3 b\u1edbt ch\u00fat th\u1eddi gian l\u1eafng nghe chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Mario Jardel, t\u00e2n binh Bolton c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u1edf Sporting Lisbon, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u00f4ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ki\u1ec7t xu\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1i t\u00ean t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng quen thu\u1ed9c nh\u01b0ng h\u00f3a ra v\u00f4 danh l\u1ea1 ho\u1eafc kia, v\u1edbi g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 non cho\u1eb9t h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chia tay Bolton n\u0103m 2010, Hunt lang b\u1ea1t qua 11 CLB tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ng\u1eafn ng\u1ee7i \u1edf Notts County. M\u00f9ng 10 th\u00e1ng B\u1ea3y n\u0103m nay, anh ph\u1ea5n kh\u1edfi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t n\u0103m v\u1edbi Crewe Alexandra, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea1ng t\u01b0 kh\u00e1c, sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i c\u0169ng trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, CLB l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd Juventus th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1eeb CLB l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t T\u00e2y Ban Nha Real Madrid, gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh 15 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi l\u00e0ng qu\u00ea Villar Perosa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh 15 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi l\u00e0ng qu\u00ea Villar Perosa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Cristiano-Ronaldo-gia-nhap-Juventus-Hanh-trinh-15-nam-ve-voi-lang-que-Villar-Perosa-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">... \u0111\u1ebfn mi\u1ec1n qu\u00ea h\u1ebbo l\u00e1nh Villar Perosa</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, ng\u00f3t ngh\u00e9t m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 r\u01b0\u1ee1i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ra \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf c\u1ea3 c\u1ea5p CLB v\u00e0 \u0110TQG c\u00f9ng h\u00e0nh trang 5 Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng hay s\u1ed1 danh hi\u1ec7u V\u0110QG c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Champions League t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, CR7 ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ea3nh t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1c xa h\u01a1n n\u1eefa so v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Old Trafford hay Santiago de Bernabeu tr\u00e1ng l\u1ec7 v\u00e0 huy\u00ean n\u00e1o. Villar Perosa l\u00e0 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a gia t\u1ed9c Agnelli tr\u1ecb v\u00ec Juventus, n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c t\u1ef1a nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i n\u00f4i c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Villar Perosa Juventus\" title=\"Villar Perosa Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/55.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>L\u00e0ng Villar Perosa \u1edf ph\u00eda b\u1eafc n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd - Qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a gia t\u1ed9c Agnelli tr\u1ecb v\u00ec Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">63 n\u0103m tr\u00f4i qua, ng\u00f4i l\u00e0ng b\u00e9 nh\u1ecf \u1edf mi\u1ec1n qu\u00ea h\u1ebbo l\u00e1nh n\u1eb1m c\u00e1ch th\u1ee7 ph\u1ee7 Turin 50km v\u1ec1 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u00e2y nam n\u00e0y l\u00e0 n\u01a1i t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c m\u00e0n giao h\u1eefu th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb, th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi t\u00ean g\u1ecdi Juventus Primavera.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n y\u00ean b\u00ecnh trong n\u0103m nay, v\u00e0 ai c\u0169ng hi\u1ec3u l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao. \u00d4 t\u00f4 r\u1ed3ng r\u1eafn n\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1eadu ngo\u00e0i th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n t\u1eeb 6 ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd b\u00f3ng l\u0103n. V\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n h\u1ebft s\u1ea1ch trong ch\u1edbp m\u1eaft. 5000 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n 1000 so v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 d\u00e2n \u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ednh \u1edf Villar Perosa, quy t\u1ee5 v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng duy nh\u1ea5t trong l\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1ea5y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ronaldo xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t v\u00e0 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh, m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 7 v\u00e0 kh\u1edfi ngu\u1ed3n cho chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng 5-0 cho c\u00e1c anh l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Massmiliano Allegri. D\u00f9 g\u00ec, \u0111\u00e1m h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tu\u1ed5i teen kia c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi Diego Godin \u1edf Sochi h\u01a1n th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ng\u00e0y Uruguay lo\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/23.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus: Ng\u00e0y si\u00eau sao ra m\u1eaft \u1edf mi\u1ec1n qu\u00ea h\u1ebbo l\u00e1nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. M\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 giao l\u01b0u v\u00e0 k\u00fd t\u1eb7ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ecb&hellip; l\u1ed9t s\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ed3 v\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfc qu\u1ea7n l\u00f3t m\u00e0 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<table cellpacing=\"0\" style=\"padding:10px 0px;\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"44px\" valign=\"top\"><img src=\"/content/images/s1.png\" alt=\"comment left\" width=\"44px\"></td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding:10px;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean mi\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf n\u00e0y, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m kho\u1ea3ng kh\u1eafc vinh quang th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u00e0 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi nhau. M\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 l\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n thi\u00eang li\u00eang v\u00e0 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111ang v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i.</em></div>\r\n            <span style=\"color: #8bc53f; float: right;\"><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Gigi Buffon, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i s\u1ed1ng Bianconeri gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Paris Saint-Germain</em></span></td>\r\n            <td width=\"44px\" valign=\"top\"><img src=\"/content/images/s2.png\" alt=\"comment right\" width=\"44px\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/river.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus: Ng\u00e0y si\u00eau sao ra m\u1eaft \u1edf mi\u1ec1n qu\u00ea h\u1ebbo l\u00e1nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Verona, Juventus &ldquo;l\u1edbn&rdquo; ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u00ean vai k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Andrea Agnelli \u0111\u00e3 ra l\u1eddi hi\u1ec7u tri\u1ec7u: <em>&ldquo;N\u0103m nay, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3.&rdquo;</em> Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Serie A hay Coppa Italia, \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap b\u1ea1c Champions League \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea9n tr\u00e1nh h\u01a1n hai th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft bu\u1ed3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1eeb Bolton \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus B, t\u1eeb th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p Manchester \u0111\u1ebfn mi\u1ec1n qu\u00ea h\u1ebbo l\u00e1nh Villar Perosa, h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p 15 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft c\u00f3 h\u1eadu cho si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 m\u1edf ra ch\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1eed m\u1edbi cho di s\u1ea3n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a gia t\u1ed9c Agnelli.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo Juventus\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/tu-bolton-den-juventus-b-hanh-trinh-su-nghiep-15-nam-cua-cristiano-ronaldo.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng Champions League cho B\u00e0 \u0110\u1ea7m Gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 0.5in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.5in;\"><strong><em>* Theo Telegraph</em></strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018:</strong><strong><br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-ronaldo-khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh-176-191424.html\">Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo: Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-den-juventus-canh-chim-bao-bao-cho-ca-serie-a-176-194051.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus: C\u00e1nh chim b\u00e1o b\u00e3o cho c\u1ea3 Serie A</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-thu-loi-tu-cristiano-ronaldo-khong-nhieu-nhu-nguoi-ta-van-nghi-176-192158.html\">Juventus thu l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta v\u1eabn ngh\u0129</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/tu-juventus-den-ac-milan-ke-hoach-tro-ve-thoi-hoang-kim-cua-serie-a-176-194193.html\">T\u1eeb Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn AC Milan: K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi ho\u00e0ng kim c\u1ee7a Serie A</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5613","checkdouble":"194602"},{"date":"08:33 18/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Monaco vs Lille 01h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (Ligue 1 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-monaco-vs-lille-01h00-ngay-198-ligue-1-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Monaco vs Lille l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (V\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Ph\u00e1p Ligue 1 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Monaco vs Lille 01h00 ng\u00e0y 198 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Monaco vs Lille 01h00 ng\u00e0y 198 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/Monaco-vs-Lille.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Monaco vs Lille</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Monaco vs Lille: 2-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 h\u00e8 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i v\u00e0 x\u00e9t t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n y\u1ebfu \u0111i so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc song Monaco v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf Ligue 1 2018/19 khi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Nantes. V\u00f2ng 2 n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Leonardo Jardim c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Louis II. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 Lille, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i trong c\u1ea3 4 m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Ligue 1, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 14 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nX\u00e9t m\u1ecdi y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1, Monaco \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt Lille v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd cps chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng n\u1eefa. Song k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 c\u1ee7a Monaco \u1edf v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t ph\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nantes \u0111ang \u1edf tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n sau khi chia tay HLV Ranieri. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 chia tay kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Fabinho, Moutinho hay Lemar. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn, HLV Jardim ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 1 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 Golovin nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLille s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00e9m Monaco nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u00ednh c\u1ea3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Rennes \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Christophe Galtier ch\u1ec9 thua 1/6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00eam nay gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n mang t\u1edbi k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. 5 m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u1eeba qua gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Monaco to\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong c\u1ea3 4 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Lille g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Ligue 1.<br>\r\n- 5 m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\n- Monaco: V\u1eafng Aleksandr Golovin (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng), Djibril Sidibe v\u00e0 Danijel Subasic; Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Adama Traore v\u00e0 Almamy Toure c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.<br>\r\n- Lille: V\u1eafng Luiz Araujo (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng).</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5612","checkdouble":"194716"},{"date":"08:18 18/08","title":"Sao Arsenal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Wenger kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/24/sao-arsenal-da-deu-thay-cu-wenger-khong-biet-huan-luyen.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f9ng Arsenal thua \u0111\u1eb9p tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Man City nh\u01b0ng trung v\u1ec7 Mustafi v\u1eabn h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i t\u00e2n HLV Emery, qua \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng v\u1edbi sang ch\u1ecdc ngo\u00e1y Gi\u00e1o S\u01b0.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">Shkodran Mustafi l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Arsene Wenger mang v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Valencia v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf Emirates, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec9nh cao \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Mustafi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 HLV Wenger v\u1edbi h\u00e0m \u00fd \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Mustafi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 HLV Wenger v\u1edbi h\u00e0m \u00fd \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/sao-arsenal-da-deu-thay-cu-wenger-khong-biet-huan-luyen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Trung v\u1ec7 Mustafi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 HLV Wenger</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00e1 kh\u1ea9m h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Unai Emery, \u0111\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Man City trong ng\u00e0y m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, khi Mustafi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh Sokratis \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2014 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t \u0111ang c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n nh\u1edd phong c\u00e1ch hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n s\u00e1t sao h\u01a1n c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u mang h\u00e0m \u00fd \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Wenger tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn derby London l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf Stamford Bridge:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">\u201cEmery n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. Th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t v\u00ec cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 b\u1ea3o t\u1eadn t\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady b\u1edfi anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd bi\u1ebft l\u00e0m g\u00ec khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 giao ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi HLV. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eabn m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i v\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c m\u00ecnh l\u00e0m.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">\u201cTr\u1eadn thua Man City th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 sao, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Chelsea ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay c\u0169ng v\u1eady. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eefng tin v\u00e0 trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec theo \u0111u\u1ed5i, tr\u00e1i ng\u1ecdt sau c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5611","checkdouble":"194710"},{"date":"07:32 18/08","title":"HLV Unai Emery nh\u1eafc Mesut Ozil t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u01a1n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-unai-emery-nhac-mesut-ozil-tich-cuc-tham-gia-phong-ngu-hon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen, HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean nh\u1eafc kh\u00e9o Mesut Ozil ph\u1ea3i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.</h2><h2>HLV Unai Emery nh\u1eafc Mesut Ozil&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Arsenal t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Arsene Wenger, HLV Unai Emery m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Arsenal ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 Manchester City v\u00e0 Chelsea, &quot;ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7&quot; \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ozil\" title=\"Ozil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/hlv-unai-emery-nhac-mesut-ozil-tich-cuc-tham-gia-phong-ngu-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Unai Emery nh\u1eafc Mesut Ozil ph\u1ea3i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u01a1n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Mesut Ozil. V\u00ec v\u1eady, \u00f4ng nh\u1eafc kh\u00e9o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u01a1n: &quot;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m. M\u00f5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;C\u00f3 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng nhau, c\u1ea3 trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u1eabn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eeb m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mesut Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf Ozil ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng HLV Unai Emery kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Mesut Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Jack Wilshere.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;V\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, Ozil c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 10, ho\u1eb7c \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i r\u1ed3i b\u00f3 v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng&quot; - Unai Emery nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: &quot;R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 anh \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e1c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Anh \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m th\u1ebf trong m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Ozil l\u00e0m g\u00ec&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Arsenal vs Chelsea s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 23h30 ng\u00e0y 18/8.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Mesut Ozil:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ozil-nhan-chi-trich-tham-te-tu-huyen-thoai-arsenal-172-194464.html\">Ozil nh\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch th\u1eadm t\u1ec7 t\u1eeb huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/neuer-phat-bieu-ve-ozil-va-quyet-dinh-giai-nghe-192-192607.html\">Neuer: &ldquo;Ozil c\u1ee9 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/a-172-192592.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u Mesut Ozil ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft &ldquo;l\u00e0m m\u00e0u&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/quoc-te/cdv-duc-bieu-tinh-bang-co-tho-nhi-ky-de-ung-ho-ozil-290-192417.html\">C\u0110V \u0110\u1ee9c bi\u1ec3u t\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng c\u1edd Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Ozil</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/tam-thu-cua-mesut-ozil-giot-nuoc-tran-ly-p2-389-192316.html\">T\u00e2m th\u01b0 c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil: Gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00e0n ly (P2)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huy-diet-psg-emery-het-loi-ca-ngoi-ozil-172-192233.html\">H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t PSG, Emery h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i Ozil</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5610","checkdouble":"194714"}]}